videos.description: Deandre Ayton catches the offensive rebound with one hand and throws it down in one motion. On the defensive end, Keanu Pinder plays volleyball with a UMBC player's shot and sends it deep into the crowd.
videos.headline: Ayton, Pinder show out in big Arizona win
